it.apice.sapere.api.space.core.strategy
Interface CustomStrategyPipelineStep<T>

Type Parameters:
T - RDF Statements iterator used by CompiledLSA
public interface CustomStrategyPipelineStep<T>

Basic interface to be implemented with a strategy to be applied in the pipeline.

Each step should take an LSA(-id) from the previous step and return an (eventually) modified version of it to be provided to the following step.

Author:
Paolo Contessi
